description: Renovated Southie Penthouse with Private Roof Deck! This updated top-floor one-bedroom offers an open, sun-filled layout with high ceilings, a crisp white kitchen featuring quartz counters, peninsula seating, and new stainless-steel appliances. The bedroom opens directly to a private roof deck — perfect for morning coffee or hosting friends. Additional features include a spacious bathroom with soaking tub, dedicated washer and dryer, and air conditioning for year-round comfort. Located just off West Broadway, you’re only steps from Southie’s best bars, restaurants, coffee shops, and more. Low $150 monthly fees, strong reserves, and no upcoming assessments. Option to purchase fully furnished provides easy move-in or rental-ready convenience. Schedule your showing today - don't wait!
